 NaCl.\n• PAA (1E6 g/mol) not easily dissolved in water\, at about 5wt% app
 ears\n  as clumpy gelly.  Tried adding NaOH pellets. Try heating in water\
 n  bath at about 60C o/n.\n• PDADMAC stock prepared at 20wt% in 0.14M NaCl
 .
